text: Valdres District Court () is a district court located in Fagernes, Valdres, Norway. It covers the municipalities of Etnedal, Nord-Aurdal, Sør-Aurdal, Vang, Vestre Slidre and Øystre Slidre, and is subordinate Eidsivating Court of Appeal.Valdres District Court ==References== == External links == *Official site .
